reviews.review_text: Best Aud source? While I went with The Brotman Schps pick for this nice show. This B n K 4011 effort also sounds wonderful.  Pretty much a tie between the two.  Several other nice sounding sources available here, but I thing the Brotman and the B n K are the two finest.
